a zm map set in a small construction area next to a subway

this map has stormy weather effects including rain and thunder which lightens the map on struck :)

there is 2 secrets 1 being a teleportation one and another being a fake wall which leads to a hole

you can also use this map for normal cs and garrys mod if you want :)


pls download and leave an assessment :)

enjoy
